Dimensions.s2cor__Description__c: Click here to see a list of your Vendors or Suppliers and their current balances.  Sage Live Vendor records can be linked to Salesforce Accounts to give a complete view of your vendors. You can create a new Sage Live Vendor by clicking on the plus symbol.
